last_episode_to_air.name: The Wedding
last_episode_to_air.overview: Can you hear those wedding bells ringing? The wedding day is finally here, and everyone is working hard for their "happily ever after"… but are they making the right choice?

name: With Love
overview: The Diaz siblings, Lily and Jorge, are on a mission to find love and purpose. They cross paths with seemingly unrelated residents during some of the most heightened days of the year—the holidays.
tagline: To joy. To familia. To life.

episodes.name: Nochebuena
episodes.overview: It’s Christmas Eve AKA “Nochebuena,” and the Diaz family gathers together for their annual celebration. Lily is dealing with a recent break-up, while her brother, Jorge Jr., is bringing a boyfriend home to meet the family. We also meet other Portland residents and see how their lives intertwine.

episodes.name: New Year's Eve
episodes.overview: It’s December 31st, which means, it’s party time! The gang attends two New Year’s Eve parties: an early one at the family home where they take part in all of the fun Latino New Year’s Eve traditions and a swanky one, where romance is in the air for everyone. Meanwhile, Sol and Miles have an unexpected first date.

episodes.name: Valentine's Day
episodes.overview: It’s “Valentine’s Day” and Lily, owning her new single life, goes to wine country by herself. However, her day of self-care is interrupted when she runs into some familiar faces. And back in Portland, things get complicated with Beatriz and her new running buddy, Leo, as Miles and Sol hit their first relationship bump.

episodes.name: Independence Day
episodes.overview: It’s the Fourth of July, and everyone’s relationship has progressed since Valentine’s Day --- some in positive ways and others negatively-- as each couple struggles with the different meanings of ‘independence.’

episodes.name: Día De Los Muertos
episodes.overview: It’s “Día De Los Muertos,” and the members of the Diaz family are forced to confront some “ghosts” from their respective pasts.

episodes.name: Christmas Eve
episodes.overview: Our happy couples get ready to enjoy Christmas Eve as the big question hangs in the air: which one of Marta’s grandbabies is gonna get married?!

episodes.name: Engagement Party
episodes.overview: Nothing brings families together like an engagement party! But as the Diaz clan wrestles with perfectionism and sobering news, they learn the best laid plans of mice and men often go awry.

episodes.name: Lily's Double Quinceañera
episodes.overview: It’s June 11th – AKA Lily’s 30th birthday! And what better way of commemorating the occasion than by tackling an old bucket list of hers… with the help of a surprising partner-in-crime.

episodes.name: Bachelor Party
episodes.overview: Viva Las Vegas! It’s Labor Day weekend and everyone’s letting loose for the bachelor party – perhaps a tad too loose as the excess of Sin City puts relationships to the test.

episodes.name: Thanksgiving
episodes.overview: It’s Thanksgiving at the Diaz home, and family and friends gather to give thanks for a wonderful year… until an unexpected dinner guest complicates things.

episodes.name: The Wedding
episodes.overview: Can you hear those wedding bells ringing? The wedding day is finally here, and everyone is working hard for their "happily ever after"… but are they making the right choice?
